name: Terra Nova DLT Gold Transaction Scene
description:
50% of proceeds will be donated to thewereachfoundation.org for Haiti's earthquake victims.

Holding the black briefcase actor Monte St. James makes a cameo appearance in "Lifestyle of a new age low key Investor." The actor is known for Just Cause (1995), The Glades (2010) and South Beach (1993). In the short film the actor is not seen at Miami's "Asian Fusion Cafe" however I thought it would be a perfect fit to combine the two photos. Members of this cast are comprised of gold, crypto, and real estate investors. Our cast was strategically assembled to showcase some of Miami's local businesses and professionals. Also local business owners make cameo appearances and product placements.
